It is not encouraging promiscuity.
Nor is it about paying the chelas and the motel, as Governor Emilio González responded when asked if there would be a distribution of condoms in his Administration.
&quot;This is not sexuality, it is best to bring condoms to those who already practice sexual activity,&quot; he said.
Keys In Jalisco
There are 13,435 accumulated cases (12,158 of AIDS and 1,317 of HIV).
